scene.message:
Ayase: Papa~?{nl}
Is this kid lost?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey there, little miss,{nl}
why are you in a place{nl}
like this? It's dangerous,{nl}
go on home now.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hey,{nl}
you think a lost child{nl}
would be in a place{nl}
like this!?{waitkey}{clearbox}Be careful!{nl}
There's no telling what{nl}
she might do!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Miss Ayase! Could you{nl}
be a bit more careful?{waitkey}{clearbox}Your carelessness has{nl}
dragged us into so much{nl}
Trouble!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Could you perhaps{nl}
learn from it a little?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Oh, shut up already!{nl}
Nitpicking everything{waitkey}{clearbox}What if she really were lost?!{nl}
Would you just leave her{nl}
to die!?{waitkey}{ret}

Black Girl: Hey~!{nl}
Can't you understand me?{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm asking whether{nl}
you've seen my papa!!{waitkey}{clearbox}He's wearing the same{nl}
clothes as you big brothers{nl}
and a black mask.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Sorry, but I don't{nl}
know any man wearing{nl}
a mask.{waitkey}{ret}

Black Girl: Huh!?{nl}
Where was he?{nl}
Tell me!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: One floor down.{nl}
He was in the student{nl}
council room.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That girl...{nl}
I feel like I've seen her{nl}
somewhere.{waitkey}{nl}
But who was she...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: I've got a weakness{nl}
for fierce-looking girls{nl}
like that.{waitkey}{ret}
